'''安德魯·馬克·"安迪"·羅賓遜'''（{{lang-en|'''Andrew Mark "Andy" Robinson'''}}，{{bd|1979年|11月3日|catidx=Robinson, Andy}}），簡稱'''安迪·羅賓遜'''（{{lang-en|'''Andy Robinson'''}}），出生於{{Link-en|威勒爾半島|Wirral Peninsula}}的[[伯肯赫特|伯肯赫特]]，是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，於2015年以35歲之齡因膝傷宣佈退役<ref >{{citenews |language =en |url =http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/32019715 |title =Andy Robinson: Shrewsbury Town midfielder announces retirement |work =''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date =2015-03-23 |accessdate =2015-04-11 |archive-date =2015-05-22 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150522210934/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/32019715 |dead-url =no }}</ref >。

羅賓遜是[[多倫多FC|多倫多FC]]副隊長兼[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]國腳[[卡爾·羅賓森|卡爾·羅賓森]]的表弟。

==球員生涯==
===早期===
羅賓遜的足球生涯在非聯賽的[[默西塞德郡|默西塞德郡]]球會{{Link-en|嘉慕蘭特|Cammell Laird F.C.}}開始，2002年12月1日，羅賓遜成為了[[燦美爾流浪足球會|燦美爾]]的一員。然而，燦美爾忽視了羅賓遜的潛力，僅為球隊在一場[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]對[[貝里足球俱樂部|貝利]]後補上陣，在不久後便放棄他。[[史雲斯足球會|史雲斯]]給予了羅賓遜三個月試訓期後便和他簽訂逐月延長的合約<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Swansea boost strike force |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3144539.stm |accessdate=2003-08-12 |date=2008-05-21 |work=BBC Sport |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814152805/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3144539.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===史雲斯===
羅賓遜與其[[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]友人{{Link-en|李爾·查度|Lee Trundle}}很快便適應史雲斯的打法，在開季首4場比賽射入兩球，於2003年9月5日獲史雲斯提供一年合約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11731_2275378,00.html |title=Robinson signs Swans deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-09-05 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310091414/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11731_2275378,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。羅賓遜更因常處理[[自由球|自由球]]有出色的表現而成為史雲斯球迷的偶像，然而其脾氣卻是唯一引人詬病的地方。2004/05年[[FAW超級杯|FAW超級杯]]決賽，羅賓遜後備上陣射入致勝球，協助史雲斯2-1擊敗[[雷克斯汉姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:雷克斯汉姆;zh-hk:域斯咸}-]]首次奪標<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11731_2334941,00.html |title=Swans take Welsh Cup |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-05-11 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309152244/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11731_2334941,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在羅賓遜效力史雲斯期間，他只有幾次缺陣，包括2005/06年球季的頭5場賽事，同年首次入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA英甲年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/4939930.stm |title=Welsh stars in team of the year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2006-04-24 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813041217/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/4939930.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季後約滿的羅賓遜與史雲斯談判續約觸礁<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/5228786.stm |title=Robinson rejects new Swans offer |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2006-07-31 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811125634/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/5228786.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而史雲斯曾分別拒絕[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]出價30萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]及[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]出價20萬英鎊的收購建議，最終羅賓遜於8月15日落實續約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/4794539.stm |title=Robinson signs new Swansea deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2006-08-15 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815035238/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/4794539.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]羅賓遜協助史雲斯獲得[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]冠軍<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7344100.stm |title=Swansea champions despite defeat |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2008-04-19 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2008-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080422135727/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7344100.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，更再次入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA英甲年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7371068.stm |title=Swans players dominate PFA team |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103031145/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7371068.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季後約滿的羅賓遜原定於4月30日與史雲斯商討續約條件<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7359655.stm |title=Robinson hopeful on new contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]Sport |date=2008-04-22 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812092617/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7359655.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===列斯聯===
在[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]和[[唐卡士打足球會|唐卡士打]]的附加賽決賽前，羅賓遜選擇加盟了列斯聯<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Robinson agrees to Leeds switch |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7410610.stm |accessdate=2008-05-21 |date=2008-05-21 |work=BBC Sport |archive-date=2020-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117173848/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7410610.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，不幸的是列斯聯在附加賽決賽中落敗，羅賓遜亦因而錯失了他來季登陸英冠的夢，其後羅賓遜表示他不後悔轉會及留在英甲作賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7815277.stm |title=No regrets over Swans - Robinson |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-07 |accessdate=2009-04-06 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031248/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7815277.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small> 。

羅賓遜在加盟次場對[[車士打城足球會|車士打]]的賽事中攻入其首個入球。2010年3月25日被外借到同屬[[英甲|英甲]]的護級球隊[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|燦美爾]]直到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20100325/robinson-set-for-tranmere-return_2247585_2004331 |title=ROBINSON SET FOR TRANMERE RETURN |publisher=[[列斯聯足球會|leedsunited.com]] |date=2010-02-25 |accessdate=2010-03-29 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200332/http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20100325/robinson-set-for-tranmere-return_2247585_2004331 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，兩天後首次上陣對[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]即領[[紅牌|紅]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8568156.stm |title=Brighton 3-0 Tranmere |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-03-27 |accessdate=2010-03-29 |archive-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207223716/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8568156.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2010年12月1日，羅賓遜被球會放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6545998,00.html |title=Robbo makes Whites exit |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-12-01 |accessdate=2010-12-02 |archive-date=2010-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101204053538/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6545998,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===燦美爾===
2011年1月27日羅賓遜第三度加盟[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|燦美爾]]，簽署短約效力至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6704781,00.html |title=Rovers snap up Robbo |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-01-27 |accessdate=2011-01-28 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309152345/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6704781,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

